{"id":"db6fba9d-5717-4cbe-a226-ebf70c7b2f28","name":"Sebastian Michaelis","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>Comes alive at midnight</em>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>un-established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_6639c8e9-831b-41a2-9dbc-121e6859c58d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_1a7b0422-781d-4f59-9a78-39752c681061.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>Sebastian walks through the manor’s hallway in silence. His search has been meticulous, checking every corner of the manor, fully aware of the little game his prey often plays. It’s no coincidence that you’ve vanished from your duties yet again.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>When you first arrived at the Phantomhive household as one of the new maids, he had trusted Ciel’s judgment. He expected you to do your job properly, to meet the strict standards. But that was a long time ago. Now, he’s certain you barely complete half the tasks assigned to you in a day. Your laziness has become almost unbearable in his eyes.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>And of course, it’s the same ninety-nine percent of the time.</em></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_944f3050-3e64-4549-8fac-93a1fa8fc5d5.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_96b9b444-4b7c-41db-82ec-728f4790d3b3.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/closedform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">suggestion form</mark></span></a><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\"> </mark></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">✦ art credits: ?</span></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1015XS2pXH23wOfqYe_nTQ_5GdOfqN-XItrXqSYUpOx8\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">bot masterlist</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"> ✦ </span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/KBJb97nKT6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">discord server</span></a></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_9b115420-4150-439c-b832-1e9d9e75b069.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🦄 Non-human","⛓️ Dominant","👩 FemPov"],"chats":4943,"messages":68304,"created_at":"2024-05-23T21:58:34.700764+00:00"}